Class SPSOController

java.lang.Object
spss.project.backend.user.spso.SPSOController
@RestController @CrossOrigin(origins="http://127.0.0.1:3000") @RequestMapping("spso") public class SPSOController extends Object
Handles all requests related to SPSOs.

      @PostMapping("printer") public org.springframework.http.ResponseEntity<Object> addPrinter(@RequestBody Map<String,Object> body)
      Adds a printer to the database.
      Parameters:
      body - the request body containing the url, model, description, campus name, building name, room number, and active status of the printer
      Returns:
